Usage: changeFloorplan [-help] [-noSnapToGrid] [[[-coreToLeft <float>][-coreToBottom <float>][-coreToRight <float>][-coreToTop <float>]] | [-coreToEdge {left bottom right top}]]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
-coreToBottom <float>                   # distance from bottom of CORE box to
                                        # bottom of DIE (float, optional)
-coreToEdge {left bottom right top}     # distance of core box left, bottom,
                                        # right and top to die (box, optional)
-coreToLeft <float>                     # distance from left of CORE box to
                                        # left of DIE. (float, optional)
-coreToRight <float>                    # distance from right of CORE box to
                                        # right of DIE (float, optional)
-coreToTop <float>                      # distance from top of CORE box to top
                                        # of DIE (float, optional)
-noSnapToGrid                           # keep user input core data without
                                        # snapping to routing track.
                                        # (bool, optional)